data.description: Looking for a gorgeous, five bedroom home on three acres in the heart of Hickory? Look no further! This move-in ready home features a bright, airy, open concept living area to entertain guests. The oversized, first floor primary suite has an updated en suite, you can relax and enjoy your in-home oasis. The upstairs has three more bedrooms, plus two bonus rooms, one of which includes an indoor climbing wall. The 3 acre lot features a small ropes course, lots of fruit trees (apples, pears, peach, pecans, etc.), many mulberry bushes, paw paws, grape vines, blackberries, and raspberries. Updates include a newer deck, new carpet and paint throughout, and updated bathrooms. In Hickory and Southeastern school district, it's country living at its finest! Come see your new home today.
